file.name: debug_api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.1.0
info:
  title: Waku REST API - Debug
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /debug/v1/info:
    get:
      summary: Get node info
      description: Retrieve information about a Waku v2 node.
      tags:
        - Debug
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Information about a Waku v2 node.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/WakuInfo'
        '5XX':
          description: Unexpected error.

components:
  schemas:
    WakuInfo:
      type: object
      properties:
        listenAddresses:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        enrUri:
          type: string
      required:
        - listenAddresses
